Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I flashily thought\NI was a goner there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Buggy the Clown, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?\NWill you team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wait is Over!\NThe Return of Captain Buggy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where are we headed, Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I smell like I farted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, we need to find my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they are now,\Nand what they're up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat for now, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Run away on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the people who got off\Nthe ship with you all back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy isn't...\NCaptain Buggy isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how long\Nit's been since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even where\NCaptain Buggy flew off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?\NWhat's the future of the Buggy Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all because of that girl\Nthief named Nami or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro... I will take\Nyour head by my own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Did you finally catch cold\Nafter always sleeping on deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gotten sick\Nbefore, only injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\NI've never had a headache myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone out there talkin'\Nabout me being a master swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's talking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Being a hottie is punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's always talking about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always felt he was a cold-hearted,\Nhorrible captain when he was well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I realize he was a bold\Nand open-hearted pirate-like pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look back, we were allowed\Nto ravage to our hearts' content
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only because we had\NCaptain Buggy's backing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, let's give the greatest and\Nflashiest funeral for Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain... Rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the rest\Nto me, Acrobat Cabaji,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Buggy Pirates' Number Two\Nand Chief of Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to rebuild the Buggy Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cabaji!\N--W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for Captain\NBuggy's successor to be me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Tamer Mohji-sama,\Nthe vice-captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain! You can stay\Nvice-captain for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna decide who gets to\Nbe captain by seeing who's stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique: Monkey Showman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique:\NCandid Camera Police Trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder at the Open-Air Steam Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll just have to fight\Nyou until your body falls apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A man-to-man fight.\NI'll take you down with these two fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:08:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! You got 'im!\N--Ooh! So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... J-Just give up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you give up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Our Captain Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Richie! Captain Richie!\NOur great captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Captain Buggy now gone,\Nthe most worthy of us to be captain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Captain Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Richie! Our great captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Richie! Captain\NRichie! Our great captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Richie! Captain Richie!\NOur great captain!...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission\Nto come onto this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do realize this island belongs\Nto us, the Bear Claw Tribe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're these guys' captain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing! Are you picking a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to shout so loud;\NI can hear you just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...super flashy\NBuggy Pirates pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this big grave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! I have a big nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling Big Nose?!\NEh?! Eh?! Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said grave! Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red?! Red, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I have a big, red nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My grave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who did this?! This is morbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention this is\Nan old wanted poster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's someone\Non the ground there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohji! Cabaji!\NWhat happened to you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Buggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so good to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what on earth happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? We suddenly got\Npunched out of the blue, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassingly enough,\Nwe can't remember a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bear Claw Tribe did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear Claw Tribe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you're going to\Nsave them, you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear Claw tribesmen are famous\Nfor being food connoisseurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain says that lions taste bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We taste bad, too!\N--I won't be very tasty at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This guy tastes way better than me!\N--Lies! Lies! He tastes much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too boney! I got nothing to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We're the Bear\NClaw Tribe! We're iron chefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some wine and spices\Nwill take your smell away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do with this food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such\Nstrange ingredients before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we boil it with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope it doesn't\Ngive me stomach trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop-Chop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chop-Chop-Chop-Chop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop-Chop-Chop\NChop-Chop-Chop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flashily reassemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain Buggy!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liven things up with\Na super flashy Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique:\NMurder at the Steam Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the beast-taming show begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can\Nhit me, Buggy the Clown-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hafta thank you all for\Neverything you did to my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I flashily come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Rice Cracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-He's doing this all for us!\N--That's our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've greatly pained you all,\Nmy adorable underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pain is nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a weird creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:20:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the hardships you had were\Nbecause of that damn Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, who might this\Npretty young woman be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget "really cute"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. I had been\Nwondering about that myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This nice woman saved\Nmy life! Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I'm sorry.\NWhat was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! The Buggy\NPirates are back in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! What is our first goal now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I think I see an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What island is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I just told you the other day!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the island where Loguetown is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty big town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it sounds like there might\Nbe a market with fresh ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hittin' up the weapon stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being stuck with one sword doesn't\Nsuit a Three Sword-Style user.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I guess I'll\Ncheck out some equipment shops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That island is where Gold Roger\Nwas born and then executed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you actually remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town where the\NKing of the Pirates died...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the city of\Nthe beginning and end...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the city where Gold Roger,\NKing of the Pirates, died!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is filled with great\Ningredients and beautiful girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Think they got any bargain sales?!\N--What are you, a housewife?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climbing the execution platform\Nand seeing the scenery comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want some swords, but...\N--Do you have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can lend you some at 300% interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Town of the Beginning and End;\NLandfall at Loguetown"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
